name: NEW KRYPTO KICKS - Series 01, #08 - "Mutagens" by RFY (HF) & FEH
description: [Felt pen, liner pen, rub-ons, and sticker collage on canvas board with digital embellishments.] Felicity (my two-year-old granddaughter) and I put this one together a few months ago, and I really enjoy the mixed media feel to this piece. To me, it looks like a radioactive livestock experiment gone horribly wrong with a dozen or more "cute and cuddly creatures" fused together into a horrible, nightmarish blob... Gotta love them nuclear mutants!  ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) & Felicity Echo Hanson (Toddler Terror)
